short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Turns off the lights on your favorite trading platform's documentation site.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Embrace the dark side with Dark Pine Docs, a subtle, eye-friendly theme for your favorite trading script documentation! This extension seamlessly transforms those glaringly bright documentation pages into a dark, sleek, and readable version, making those lengthy coding sessions substantially more comfortable for your eyes. Please note: This extension is independently developed and has no affiliation with any trading platforms or scripting languages.
